nodes.text: Dalna was a planet located in the Dalnan sector in the Outer Rim Territories inhabited by the Dalnans. The planet was known for its agriculture and its waterfalls. During the High Republic Era, the planet was considering joining the Galactic Republic, and a Dalnan delegation that included Ambassador Weft intended to travel to the Starlight Beacon. As the Padawan of the Jedi Master Dooku, Qui-Gon Jinn visited the waterfalls of Dalna.
